      "target": "<stage>interest</stage>\n<intent_label>confirm_choice</intent_label>\n<visual_summary>顾客在两个商品之间来回比较，说明已经进入备选项评估。 当前场景是服装陈列区，可见判断应围绕两个候选项在版型、面料、颜色、尺码、护理方式和价格差异上的差异。视角为导购可观察中近距离视角。</visual_summary>\n<engagement_pattern>顾客注意力在两个具体选项之间切换。 移动围绕两个商品点位展开，不是离开式移动。 比较行为集中在版型、面料、颜色、尺码、护理方式和价格差异，说明选择尚未收敛。</engagement_pattern>\n<gaze_and_attention>视线在两个商品或对应价签之间来回移动。 视线切换应被解释为对版型、面料、颜色、尺码、护理方式和价格差异的对照。</gaze_and_attention>\n<body_and_hands>身体朝向两个备选商品之间的区域。 手部可能指向、拿起或靠近两个备选商品。 手部或身体在两个选项之间移动，说明还没有锁定单一商品。</body_and_hands>\n<belief>Two options remain close, and the decisive difference is not yet clear.</belief>\n<desire>confirm the preferred choice</desire>\n<intention>move toward confirming the choice</intention>",
      "prediction": "<stage>interest</stage>\n<intent_label>explore_options</intent_label>\n<visual_summary>The customer is examining two vases on display.</visual_summary>\n<engagement_pattern>The customer is standing still, focused on the vases.</engagement_pattern>\n<gaze_and_attention>The customer is looking at the white vase with a reflective surface.</gaze_and_attention>\n<body_and_hands>The customer is reaching out towards the white vase, possibly to touch it or get a closer look.</body_and_hands>\n<belief>The customer is interested in the white vase due to its reflective surface.</belief>\n<desire>The customer wants to know more about the white vase or consider purchasing it.</desire>\n<intention>The customer intends to explore the options further, possibly to make a decision about the white vase.</intention>",
